10 threat; or
11 3. Sharing the confidential information with the express
12 authority of the Homeland Security Advisor or designee of the
13 Homeland Security Advisor.
14 D. Information collected or disseminated under the authority of
15 this section shall be privileged and not discoverable nor subject to
